{"tid":528912,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解啲工人姐姐語文能力咁勁","createTime":"2018-01-14T11:04:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-15T04:54:10.000Z","uid":82917,"like":53,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"4b499d47efdce18328d99a9ad1c5038809707322","tid":528912,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T11:04:43.000Z","msg":"學幾年就識聽識講九成廣東話<br />\n仲要文法冇錯<br />\n雖然完全唔識睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好撚勁秋 有啲連電視都睇得明每集講緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有啲姐姐專係講英文 「lak」「lak」聲之餘仲以為佢外國留過學<br />\n<br />\n到底佢地點學架呢？英文就話學校可能有教（但如果用英文教學屋企應該都有啲米唔洗黎香港做工人姐姐）<br />\n但廣東話真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好有語言天份<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雙語教學多年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有啲人連一句完整英文都講唔出淨係識this this this<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自愧不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c51fa76a298379f77baf40546235ae5b84e82a5e","tid":528912,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T11:09:18.000Z","msg":"有無人屋企有工人姐姐"},{"pid":"0f44e560cafc03f6bd24a41a7c0a98379bcd4a35","tid":528912,"uid":16775,"like":47,"dislike":5,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T11:09:28.000Z","msg":"黎得個啲全部大學生黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b8614138db1991363cd7fa233b51bf467f5665d","tid":528912,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T11:09:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55a3396e2833dcf284740019ce00a7d008cc0827","tid":528912,"uid":134774,"like":0,"disli